OL,5, Tax cuts, due to be announced on       
OL,6, Friday, are likely to push UK borrowing
OL,7, and debt to unsustainable levels, a    
OL,8, leading economic think tank has warned.
OL,10,FThe UK will spend billions helping     
OL,11,Fhouseholds and firms with energy bills,
OL,12,Fbut tax cuts will have a longer-term   
OL,13,Fimpact on public finances, the         
OL,14,FInstitute for Fiscal Studies said.     
OL,16,FEven after that support ends, the UK   
OL,17,Fwill borrow #100bn a year, it says.    
OL,19,FTax cuts amounted to a "gamble" that   
OL,20,Fmay not pay off, the IFS warned.       
